23.teamComment: BMS is home to many songs that many people are not even aware of their origins.It's time we give back what we have received and show appreciation for BMS.Let's celebrate an amazing 20 years of BOF and 26 years of BMS!42SoL：「A reality like a mirage. Disturb.」DawMii：「I need money kudasai」Dazuko：「You Literally Use Fucking Bitwig」eili：「I can sing pretty fast in English seeing as how I am just generic white bread.」L216：「I, L216, the Beatific Meme Scaler, descend upon this team of the so-called Be-Music Source format of structured play by the call of fate an— Oh, you are also a Be-Music Source aficionado from another world? Very well, I grant you permission to play with me.」Len：「The meaning of life, one is not meant to searched but realized」LuvTek：「KBSP2009가 15년이나 되었다니 믿을 수가 없읍니다.」Medium：「Falling, yet floating. Dragged away, yet continuing forward. Life is ironic, yet it’s Schrödinger-like state is still enjoyable through music. Now, reach and grip the star…」Melone：「underway at the edge of the cosmos」NASA：「PATTERNER'S DELIGHT」nor：「」Nos：「」OfficialAz3：「i want iidx controller」Phrygia：「BMS (Be-Music Script) is 1998年にやねうらおに 의해 개발된 file format for 리ゲー。 ...wait this is completely unrelated to my role (dies)」rime：「あっ」RipLeEpic：「imagine taking time to type a quote. wait...」Small Meeks：「my secret ingredient in bolognese is arsenic」Tiv：「譜面を作るのだ」tkqn14：「cocoa.」Warlock：「This is a quote」WIC：「8年ぶりに帰ってきました」エシャ：「this exists」七海：「I'm BMS Noob...」

28.teamComment: 「涙に濡れ、現わるは透明で、繊細すぎる感傷」チーム名はディフラグメントと読みます。Diphylleia(サンカヨウ属)＋Fragment(破片)の造語で、砕け散ったガラスの破片とサンカヨウの花を足したような意味がありますちなみに、サンカヨウの花は水に濡れると透明になるという唯一無二の特徴を持つ花です　透明な姿はヒビ割れたガラスみたいでキレイだったりそんな感じで、サンカヨウの花のような繊細で儚げな楽曲を作っていけたらなぁと思います
